## 🚀 Quick Start (5 Minutes)

### Prerequisites
```bash
node --version  # Need v16+
npm --version   # Need v8+
```

Don't have Node.js? → Download from https://nodejs.org/

### Installation

**Step 1: Navigate to Project**
```bash
cd C:\Users\sujal\OneDrive\Desktop\travelProject
```

**Step 2: Backend Setup (Terminal 1)**
```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start
```
✅ See: "🚀 Server running on port 5000"

**Step 3: Frontend Setup (Terminal 2 - NEW WINDOW)**
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```
✅ Browser opens at http://localhost:3000

**Step 4: Test It Works**
1. Click "Journey Planner"
2. Click "Bhayandar" (Origin)
3. Click "Churchgate" (Destination)
4. Click "Find Routes"
5. See 2-3 routes appear! 🎉

**Need help?** See [QUICKSTART.md](QUICKSTART.md) or [SETUP_GUIDE.md](SETUP_GUIDE.md)

