## 📡 API Overview

### Core Endpoints

```http
POST /api/journey/plan
→ Plan multi-modal journey

GET /api/realtime/platform/:station/:mode
→ Live platform information

GET /api/analytics/popular-routes
→ Usage statistics

GET /api/disruptions/active
→ Current service issues

# External helper endpoints (example)
GET /api/external/reverse?lat=<>&lon=<> → Reverse geocode (Nominatim)
GET /api/external/weather?lat=<>&lon=<> → Current weather (OpenWeatherMap)
GET /api/external/convert?amount=&from=&to= → Currency conversion (exchangerate.host)
GET /api/external/ip?ip=<> → IP -> location (ipapi.co)
```

### WebSocket Events

```javascript
// Real-time updates every 30s
socket.on('disruption_alert', ...)
socket.on('crowd_update', ...)
socket.on('position_update', ...)
```

**Full API docs:** [API_DOCUMENTATION.md](API_DOCUMENTATION.md)

