## ⚙️ Configuration

### Backend (.env)
```env
PORT=5000
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
NODE_ENV=development
# Optional GTFS-RT example
# GTFS_RT_CITY=mumbai
# GTFS_RT_FEED_URL=https://api.example.com/gtfs-rt
```

### Frontend (.env)
```env
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

**Templates:** `.env.example` files included

